Talulah Riley https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Talulah_Riley 0 Talulah Jane Riley-Milburn (born 26 September 1985), known professionally as Talulah Riley, is an English actress. She has appeared in films such as Pride Prejudice, St Trinian's, The Boat That Rocked, St Trinian's 2: The Legend of Fritton's Gold, and Inception. She currently portrays Angela in the HBO science-fiction western television series Westworld.
